Ford Motor Credit Co , unit Ford Motor Co , raising 250 mln dlrs via offering note due 1990 yielding 6.95 pct , said lead underwriter Goldman Sachs .
The note 6-7/8 pct coupon priced 99.80 yield 47 basis point comparable Treasury security .
Non-callable life , issue rated A-1 Moody's AA Standard Poor 's .
On October 7 , 1986 , credit unit sold 200 mln dlrs same-maturity note , rated A-1/A , priced yield 7.172 pct 77 basis point Treasuries .
